§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We name a probability density which is a constant function
    over some interval of real numbers. ⦉
⦉

§ What ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ A ❬uniform density❭ on the inveral $[a, b]$ is the density
    which has constant value $b - a$. ⦉

  ‖ The ❬standard uniform density❭ is the uniform density on
    $[0, 1]$ ⦉
⦉

